### 1. Trigger the Audit
# @name triggerAudit
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticker": "TSLA"
}

### 2. Check the Result
# Use the task_id from the response above
@taskId = {{triggerAudit.response.body.task_id}}

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/audit/{{taskId}}